definitions.definition: Any of various large, venomous rays , of the orders Rajiformes and Myliobatiformes , having a barbed , whiplike tail .
A device that simulates a cell tower , used to intercept cell phone communications .

main_definition: Any of various large, venomous rays , of the orders Rajiformes and Myliobatiformes , having a barbed , whiplike tail .
secondary_definitions: ( US law enforcement ) A device that simulates a cell tower , used to intercept cell phone communications .
